Frequently Asked Questions – FAQs
Q1
How to write 5000 in words?
5000 in words is written as Five thousand.

Q2
If 5000 is Five-thousand, then 15000 is?
15000 in words is written as Fifteen thousand.

Q3
What is 45000 in English?
45,000 is written as Forty-five thousand in words.

Q4
Is 5000 a perfect square or a non-perfect square?
5000 is a non-perfect square number.

Q5
Is 5000 an odd number or even number?
5000 is an even number because it is wholly divisible by 2.

Q6
Is 5000 a prime number or composite number?
5000 is a composite number.

