5	000
Five	Thousand
5000 in English
English is the most common language used worldwide for education. Hence, it is necessary to learn the numbers also in English. The spelling of 5000 in English is Five thousand.

What is 5000?
In Maths, 5000 is a numeral that expresses a value or a count. The numeral 5000 is written as Five thousand in words. Other specifications of the number 5000 are:

5000 is a cardinal number
5000 is an even number
5000 is a natural number
5000 is a whole number
5000 is a composite number
